sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>PacketInspectorPage
    participant API1 as DRF<br/>StartCaptureView
    participant API2 as DRF<br/>CaptureStatusView
    participant Task as capture_packets_task
    participant Celery as Celery Worker
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Click "Start Capture"
    FE->>API1: POST /api/capture/start/ {interface: "eth0"}
    API1->>DB: CaptureSession.objects.create(status="running", interface="eth0")
    API1->>Celery: capture_packets_task.delay(session_id)
    Celery->>Task: Start Scapy sniff()
    API1-->>FE: 200 OK {session_id, status: "running"}
    FE-->>U: Display "Capture running" status
    U->>FE: Check capture status
    FE->>API2: GET /api/capture/status/
    API2->>DB: CaptureSession.objects.latest()
    DB-->>API2: Session with packet count
    API2-->>FE: 200 OK {status, packets_captured, duration}
    FE-->>U: Display live capture metrics
